      "repair_reason": "- [P1] Manual review is needed because the remaining blockers are contributor real-behavior proof and maintainer security/product direction, not a narrow automated code repair.; Needs attention: Needs attention because the diff changes native tool approval fallback behavior around a security boundary. (sha=7fefd4bc89d138d396097f0b5473a5523fd479c9)",
      "review_summary": "The branch changes stale native hook direct-bridge errors to fall through to gateway RPC, changes Codex app-server native relay invocation failures to generic before_tool_call policy fallback, and updates focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +1, Tests -13. Total -12 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: Partially: source and tests show current stale/unavailable relay paths hard-deny, but this review did not run the reported WSL2/Docker gateway restart or drain scenario.",
