      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): regenerate native hook descriptors when relay unavailable after restart",
        "body": "## Problem\nNative hook direct-bridge errors hard-deny when relay is unavailable after gateway restart. Stale native hook descriptors are not regenerated, and Codex app-server relay invocation failures do not fall back to generic OpenClaw before-tool-call policy.\n\nFixes #89325\n\n## Root Cause\nStale native hook descriptors were treated as hard errors instead of falling through to gateway RPC. Codex app-server relay invocation failures had no fallback to generic OpenClaw policy evaluation.\n\n## Fix\nChange stale native hook direct-bridge errors to fall through to gateway RPC instead of hard-denying. Change Codex app-server relay invocation failures to fall back to generic OpenClaw before-tool-call policy evaluation.\n\n## Real Behavior Proof\n\n- **Behavior addressed**: Native hook descriptors became stale after gateway restart, causing hard-deny errors instead of regenerating. Codex app-server relay invocation failures rejected tool calls without policy fallback.\n- **Real environment tested**: Linux (Node.js 22), openclaw development checkout with pnpm, vitest 4.1.8.\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch**:\n  1. `node ./node_modules/.bin/vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.cli.config.ts src/cli/native-hook-relay-cli.test.ts`\n  2. `node ./node_modules/.bin/vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-codex.config.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts`\n- **Evidence after fix**:\n```\n$ node ./node_modules/.bin/vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.cli.config.ts src/cli/native-hook-relay-cli.test.ts\n\n RUN  v4.1.8 /home/user/openclaw\n\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  20 passed (20)\n   Duration  7.23s\n\n$ node ./node_modules/.bin/vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-codex.config.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts\n\n RUN  v4.1.8 /home/user/openclaw\n\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  64 passed (64)\n   Duration  26.19s\n```\n- **Observed result after fix**: All 84 tests pass (20 CLI native hook relay + 64 Codex approval bridge). Tests cover relay regeneration on unavailable relay, fallback from stale descriptors to gateway RPC, and Codex app-server fallback to generic before-tool-call policy.\n- **What was not tested**: Live gateway restart with active native hook relay was not manually tested end-to-end. The tests verify the code paths for relay regeneration and fallback policy evaluation in isolation.",
        "branch": "fix/native-hook-relay-regeneration-89325",
